Document: VisualShaderNodeParticleConeVelocity
Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodeparticleconevelocity.rst
Summary: This node defines initial particle velocity in a cone shape starting from the center with a given spread, used in the "start" step of particle shaders.

Description
This node can be used in "start" step of particle shader. It defines the initial velocity of the particles, making them move in cone shape starting from the center, with a given spread.